channel.title: WonderWDFscapE - Codename: Lost City
channel.description:
[center][b]WonderWDFscapE[/b][/center]
[b]Introduction: [/b]WonderWDFscapE used to be my old (old) Private runescape sever, when i first joined here at Moparscape, Then I gave up on my sever, the reason was: Im plain ol' lazy. some people might remember this awesome sever (/over-exaduration) Some of you may not.
[b]Why did you make this thread:[/b] Im proud to announce, The Re-Opening of WonderWDFscapE! Codenamed Lost City. (Because WonderWDFscapE was lost for some time :P)
[b]So...?[/b] Anyone wanna help me remake this awesome sever?
[b]Yep![/b] Okays then, Basically i want the sever not to look like everyone elses,, I Want it set in a sort of really textured city in RuneScape (For example, Tzhar, or the Lost City place :P)
So if anyone could help. Please do.
The sever is planned to be released in 3 days from now. [br][size=1]Posted on: April 25, 2007, 09:21:11 AM[/size][hr]BYW, im not active on Moparscape, But i might become. Also just so you know, Ma name is Wonderguy6.
